name: Duskfall's Dissociated Open Ended Journey
description:
If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

Discord: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

A Blended mix of my two models:

Duskfall AI, The Duskfall Portal Crew (duskfalltest) and of course: Openjourney (Midjourney-V4)

This model has HIGH synthwave and POP PUNK sort of aesthetic, just due to the amount of dusk and vaporwave and sythwave colors were in the Duskfall models prior.

pink haired woman with cat ears and green eyes
(This run was done by our friend who's been testing the new models for us)

Steps: 20, Sampler: Euler a, CFG scale: 7, Seed: 3137319504, Face restoration: CodeFormer, Size: 512x512, Model hash: ea0bb8fb34, Model: Duskfall's Dissociated Journey, Batch size: 2, Batch pos: 0

This is trained largely on a small data set of our own art with a focus on the fact that our art, and any stable/midjourney outputs we included in this are related to our Dissociative Identity Disorder.

DO NOT RESELL THIS MODEL, AS IT DOES HAVE A TON OF MY ART IN IT. You may:

  • Merge, use at will

  • SELL your generations - it's a STYLE after all!

  • Do credit when reuploading or merging if possible.

  • DO USE in any merged, OR home based model - cause that's what it's for!

  • Don't resell the model, because HEY 1/3rd of it or more we don't own (Stable, Openjourney)

P.s. The really silly "OBJECTS" Grid was done by our 67 year old mother. (The one in the examples thing, because formatting the description of this one was a hellscape today)

modelVersions.description: This has a baked in VAE because we didn't use hugging face to make this one, we AHEM blew our debit card out the water and cried. Also thank you god for Open Journey because it made our model even cooler. Has our two models, plus Prompt Hero's OpenJourney.
